Item 2.02 Results of Operations and Financial
Condition. On April 16, 2021, Morgan Stanley
(the "Company") released financial information
with respect to its quarter ended March 31,
2021. A copy of the press release containing
this information is annexed as Exhibit 99.1 to
this Report and by this reference incorporated
herein and made a part hereof. In addition, a
copy of the Company's Financial Data
Supplement for its quarter ended March 31,
2021 is annexed as Exhibit 99.2 to this Report
and by this reference incorporated herein and
made a part hereof. The information furnished
under Item 2.02 of this Report, including
Exhibit 99.1 and Exhibit 99.2, shall be deemed
to be "filed" for purposes of the Securities
Exchange Act of 1934, as amended. Item 9.01
